trans-unit.source: <see cref="T:System.Activities.Hosting.SymbolResolver" /> is an extension for providing a host <see cref="T:System.Activities.LocationReferenceEnvironment" /> containing objects that can be dereferenced by a string name.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Activities.Hosting.SymbolResolver" /> 是一种用于提供宿主 <see cref="T:System.Activities.LocationReferenceEnvironment" />（包含可通过字符串名称取消引用的对象）的扩展。

trans-unit.source: Values provided through a <see cref="T:System.Activities.Hosting.SymbolResolver" /> are not persisted.
trans-unit.target: 不会保留通过 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Hosting.SymbolResolver" /> 提供的值。

trans-unit.source: Persistence of <see cref="T:System.Activities.Hosting.SymbolResolver" /> values is a host responsibility.
trans-unit.target: 宿主负责保留 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Hosting.SymbolResolver" /> 值。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Hosting.SymbolResolver" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Hosting.SymbolResolver" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: Adds an object reference to the dictionary of symbols keyed by string name.

trans-unit.target: 符号的名称。

trans-unit.source: The value of the symbol to reference.
trans-unit.target: 要引用的符号的值。

trans-unit.source: Adds a symbol using the specified symbol name and value.
trans-unit.target: 使用指定的符号名称和值添加符号。

trans-unit.source: The name of the symbol.

trans-unit.target: 使用指定的符号名称和类型添加符号。

trans-unit.target: 将使用指定类型的默认值添加符号。

trans-unit.source: Returns a <see cref="T:System.Activities.LocationReferenceEnvironment" /> instance that enables access to references of symbol values in <see cref="T:System.Activities.Hosting.SymbolResolver" /> represented as <see cref="T:System.Activities.LocationReference" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: 返回 <see cref="T:System.Activities.LocationReferenceEnvironment" /> 实例，利用该实例可访问 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Hosting.SymbolResolver" /> 中以 <see cref="T:System.Activities.LocationReference" /> 对象形式表示的符号值引用。

trans-unit.source: A location reference that enables access to references to symbol values in <see cref="T:System.Activities.Hosting.SymbolResolver" /> represented as <see cref="T:System.Activities.LocationReference" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: 一个位置引用，利用它可以访问 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Hosting.SymbolResolver" /> 中以 <see cref="T:System.Activities.LocationReference" /> 对象形式表示的符号值引用。

trans-unit.source: Removes all symbols from the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Hosting.SymbolResolver" />.
trans-unit.target: 从 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Hosting.SymbolResolver" /> 中移除所有符号。

trans-unit.target: 要在 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Hosting.SymbolResolver" /> 中查找的键/值对形式的符号。

trans-unit.target: 返回一个值，该值指示 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Hosting.SymbolResolver" /> 是否包含指定的符号。

trans-unit.target: 如果 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Hosting.SymbolResolver" /> 包含指定的符号，则为 <see langword="true" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.target: 要将符号复制到其中的键/值对一维数组。

trans-unit.target: 目标数组中从零开始的索引，在此处开始复制。

trans-unit.target: 将 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Hosting.SymbolResolver" /> 中的符号复制到现有的键/值对一维数组，从指定的数组索引处开始。
